                <summary>The Board of Education, upon nomination of Jed Hotchkiss, County
                    Superintendent for Augusta Schools, appointed School Trustees for county
                    townships. City of Staunton: Maj. H. M. Bell, William J. Nelson, P. Byron Hoge.
                    Beverly Manor Township: John Towberman, Col. Asher W. Harman, Leigh R. Waddell.
                    Pastures Township: B. O Ferguson, James H. Heiser, John S. Guy. Riverheads
                    Township: C. H. Withrow, Rev. C. Beard, Dr. J. M. Watson. Middle River: William
                    Wilson, Kasper B. Koiner, B. J. Craig. North River: Dr. William H. Davies,
                    Samuel Forrer, Joseph Plecker.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
